def time_write(self):
    N = 1_000_000
    table_bytes = BytesIO()
    t = Table()
    t['floats'] = np.random.random(N)
    t['ints'] = np.random.randint(0, 100, N)
    t['strings'] = b'some strings'
    t['booleans'] = t['floats'] > 0.5
    t.write(table_bytes, format='fits')
